Name: Plan Z
About the game: Plan Z A game in which the world plunged into war after the spread of an unknown virus. You must survive until wave 11 to be picked up by a rescue helicopter. Get special currency from killing monsters so you can buy weapons, ammo, turrets, and grenades. You can team up with other people or your friends to confront hordes of enemies.
